Get Mesh Blocks (2021 edition) polygons

get_mb21_poly.Rd

Get Mesh Blocks (2021 edition) polygons

Usage

get_mb21_poly(export_dir = tempdir())

Arguments

export_dir

The directory to store the downloaded data.

Value

A sf object.

Examples

get_mb21_poly()
